{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f9356ab3b2","title":"对河北省委关于解决水利问题的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c671bedcb9","index":0,"year":1959,"month":10,"day":10,"articleId":"f9356ab3b2"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"2354993efd","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"f9356ab3b2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"震林，即谭震林，当时任中共中央书记处书记、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"2c00bca39b","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"f9356ab3b2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共河北省委1959年10月6日关于解决河北省水利问题给毛泽东并中央的报告。报告说，为了具体贯彻执行我们今后3年的经济建设方针，从1960年至1962年，在水利上我们需要做好3件事：首先解决洪水灾害问题；其次解决沥水灾害问题；与此同时基本实现农田水利化。为此共需国家投资12.7亿元，每年平均4亿元左右。"}],"contents":[{"id":"89cfeba9bf","type":"title","text":"对河北省委关于解决水利问题的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"f9356ab3b2"},{"id":"2354993efd","type":"paragraph","text":"震林同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"f9356ab3b2"},{"id":"2c00bca39b","type":"paragraph","text":"此件以看了，请提到书记处会议上谈一下，予以批准。投资问题，请与有关部门及总理研究一下，然后确定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"f9356ab3b2"},{"id":"99575356f8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"f9356ab3b2"},{"id":"a2bb89c244","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"f9356ab3b2"}],"page":{"id":"fae97e630b","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"f9356ab3b2","start":434,"end":434}}}},"__N_SSG":true}